    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>《最后指令：Prologue》</strong>中，玩家可以体验到《最后指令》主游戏的特别序章。<br><br>《最后指令》是一款受到经典贪食蛇启发的弹幕动作冒险RPG！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类完成最终进化，曾经为人类服务的智慧程式们，在这个全面数位化的世界中生活，并思考它们存在的意义...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>贪吃蛇 x 动作弹幕，经典游戏新体验！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《最后指令 Last Command》是一款结合经典游戏贪吃蛇与弹幕要素的全新动作游戏，你必须操作PYTHON爬虫程式，在闪躲敌人弹幕的同时，收集散落的资料点对敌人造成伤害。在惊险且丰富的头目战中取得胜利，强化你的爬虫程式并揭开程式世界的秘密！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/25fa1ed278fd7eb6649d6732569439bb.poster.avif?t=1730101282\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/25fa1ed278fd7eb6649d6732569439bb.webm?t=1730101282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/25fa1ed278fd7eb6649d6732569439bb.mp4?t=1730101282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▉ 《最后指令 Last Command》的基本操作承袭自经典游戏贪吃蛇，并加入了「冲刺」与「解析」两种新动作，玩家需要善用新动作灵活操作贪吃蛇闪避敌人的攻击、收集关卡生成的「资料」来对敌人造成伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/59a8f1112564a22b3bd9ef9dcee329ec.poster.avif?t=1730101282\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/59a8f1112564a22b3bd9ef9dcee329ec.webm?t=1730101282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/59a8f1112564a22b3bd9ef9dcee329ec.mp4?t=1730101282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▉ 数量众多且不重複的头目战，各有独特的造型与攻击手段，从琳琅满目的全版弹幕，乃至绝处逢生的空间障碍，考验你应对各种难关的反应能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/9f86d776f35c954ad5aa5e1bc2050840.poster.avif?t=1730101282\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/9f86d776f35c954ad5aa5e1bc2050840.webm?t=1730101282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/9f86d776f35c954ad5aa5e1bc2050840.mp4?t=1730101282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▉ 模组将赋予程式众多特殊能力，随着游戏的推进，获得的模组种类也会随之增加。装备不同的模组，找出属于自己的最佳组合攻克难关吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/d4b2db83d80280dc6baf4376eab6722d.poster.avif?t=1730101282\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/d4b2db83d80280dc6baf4376eab6722d.webm?t=1730101282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/d4b2db83d80280dc6baf4376eab6722d.mp4?t=1730101282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▉ 探索广大的程式世界，越过危险，挑战难关，发掘人类消失后这世界所隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/08dce79e635fcbde10fa6c598a83bc21.poster.avif?t=1730101282\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/08dce79e635fcbde10fa6c598a83bc21.webm?t=1730101282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029810/extras/08dce79e635fcbde10fa6c598a83bc21.mp4?t=1730101282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
